-- Ontario Teachers' plans to increase stake in Bristol Airport
-- By Andrea Hopkins
-- Mon Jul 28, 2014 01:11PM EDT
-- None



TORONTO, July 28 (Reuters) - Canada's Ontario Teachers' Pension Plan said on Monday it plans to increase its ownership of Britain's Bristol Airport from the current 49 percent as Australian asset manager Macquarie Group <MQG.AX> reportedly shops for buyers for its 50 percent stake.

